Criterion 6_Attracts or Retains Businesses which Provide Essential Services.

 Consideration will be given to proposed programs which will address the attraction or retention of businesses commonly
associated with neighborhood needs (corner grocery stores, dry cleaners, pharmacies, etc.). The applicant must
describe clearly the nature and anticipated impact of activities. Documentation in the form of letters from existing
