should be provided to demonstrate clearly and objectively that without the proposed CDBG Program, existing retail/commercial
businesses would curtail their operations. The applicant also must document and address the potential impact of
the business loss on the community and/or target area. HUD would accept as examples of clear and objective evidence
a notice issued by the business to affected employees, a public announcement by the business, or financial records
