 None. 


Comments:

 Two commenters recommended that the priority emphasize human resource development principles. 


Discussion:

 The Secretary believes that the provision of quality post-employment training that will maintain or upgrade the
skills of persons engaged in community rehabilitation programs is career enhancing and reflective of human resource
development principles. 


