 None. 


Comments:

 One commenter expressed concern that the priority will not provide training opportunities for professional persons,
such as vocational evaluators and work adjustment personnel, who are employed by community rehabilitation programs.



Discussion:

 The Secretary notes that the priority addresses the need for ongoing post-employment training for all personnel
employed by community rehabilitation programs. 


